Class DialogContainerStartGame

java.lang.Object
cc.jayv.monopoly3.DialogContainer
cc.jayv.monopoly3.DialogContainerStartGame
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class DialogContainerStartGame extends DialogContainer implements Serializable
Dialog, Start Game: An optional dialog that allows the user to configure basic game settings, and start the game when ready.
Provides options for player count and custom player names; allows starting the game.
